<Link id="l00174" /><CodeLine lineNumber="174"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// A class that can track all registers with locations in a UnwindRow object.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00175" /><CodeLine lineNumber="175"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00176" /><CodeLine lineNumber="176"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Register locations use a map where the key is the register number and the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00177" /><CodeLine lineNumber="177"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// the value is a UnwindLocation.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00178" /><CodeLine lineNumber="178"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00179" /><CodeLine lineNumber="179"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// The register maps are put into a class so that all register locations can</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00182" /><CodeLine lineNumber="182" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/registerlocations"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">class </span><span class="doxyHighlight"><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/registerlocations">RegisterLocations</a> &#123;</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00184" /><CodeLine lineNumber="184"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00185" /><CodeLine lineNumber="185"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">public</span><span class="doxyHighlight">:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00186" /><CodeLine lineNumber="186"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Return the location for the register in \\a RegNum if there is a location.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00187" /><CodeLine lineNumber="187"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00188" /><CodeLine lineNumber="188"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// \\param RegNum the register number to find a location for.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00189" /><CodeLine lineNumber="189"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00190" /><CodeLine lineNumber="190"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// \\returns A location if one is available for \\a RegNum, or std::nullopt</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00191" /><CodeLine lineNumber="191"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// otherwise.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00192" /><CodeLine lineNumber="192" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/registerlocations/#a71d46b6c55ac8973987d21a7809ff271"><span class="doxyHighlight">  std::optional&lt;UnwindLocation&gt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/registerlocations/#a71d46b6c55ac8973987d21a7809ff271">getRegisterLocation</a>(uint32&#95;t RegNum)</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword"> const </span><span class="doxyHighlight">&#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00193" /><CodeLine lineNumber="193"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">auto</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> Pos = Locations.find(RegNum);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00194" /><CodeLine lineNumber="194"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Pos == Locations.end())</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00195" /><CodeLine lineNumber="195"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> std::nullopt;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00196" /><CodeLine lineNumber="196"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> Pos-&gt;second;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00197" /><CodeLine lineNumber="197"><span class="doxyHighlight">  &#125;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00198" /><CodeLine lineNumber="198"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00199" /><CodeLine lineNumber="199"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Set the location for the register in \\a RegNum to \\a Location.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00200" /><CodeLine lineNumber="200"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00202" /><CodeLine lineNumber="202"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00203" /><CodeLine lineNumber="203"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// \\param Location the UnwindLocation that describes how to unwind the value.</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00241" /><CodeLine lineNumber="241"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00242" /><CodeLine lineNumber="242"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// The row consists of an optional address, the rule to unwind the CFA and all</span></CodeLine>
